## Third-Party Licenses

This project includes or depends on third-party software with the following licenses:

### rang (Header-only colored output library)
- **Repository**: https://github.com/agauniyal/rang
- **License**: Unlicense (Public Domain)
- **Usage**: Terminal color output functionality

### Boost C++ Libraries (Selected Components)
- **Repository**: https://github.com/boostorg/boost
- **License**: Boost Software License 1.0
- **Usage**: System utilities and filesystem operations
- **Components Used**: system, filesystem, config, core

### Google Test (GTest)
- **Repository**: https://github.com/google/googletest
- **License**: BSD 3-Clause License
- **Usage**: Testing framework (development dependency)

### PyClaudeCli (Optional Runtime Dependency)
- **License**: Check individual PyClaudeCli project for license terms
- **Usage**: Claude AI integration backend

